title: One Day Teen Patti Classic
description:
Let your players experience the highs and lows of one day teen patti in this three card poker card game. 
Back the favourite or choose to go for the outsider, this sensationally tense and exciting game provides 
the full exhilaration and emotion of surprise wins and bad beats! 
Like our original teen patti version, players get to choose between Player A and Player B but this game 
packs a punch. 
Ezugi have introduced the back and lay functionality made famous in betting exchanges. Before each 
card is drawn, odds change based on the current favourite hand allowing players time to observe, bet 
again, change their mind by backing or laying the other side! It is possible for players to trade their way 
to a winning position no matter what the outcome!
